stork.module.ftp

Class FTPListParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • stork.feather.Bell<Stat>
      • stork.module.ftp.FTPListParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.concurrent.Future<Stat>

    public class FTPListParser
extends Bell<Stat>
    A class for parsing FTP listings. Based heavily on Mozilla's own FTP list parsing code, available in their mozilla-central repository, under the path:

    netwerk/streamconv/converters/ParseFTPList.cpp

    This parser will return a tree root that has its name set if and only if information about the listed directory was able to be retrieved from the listing results.
